\prod_n\left(1+\frac{i}{n}\right)
\prod_n\left\vert 1+\frac{i}{n}\right\vert
\prod (1+z_k) 
\iff
\sum\log (1+z_k)
|1+\frac{i}{n}| = (1+\frac{1}{n^2})^{1/2}
\prod_n  |1+\frac{i}{n}|
\Leftrightarrow \sum_n \log{|1+\frac{i}{n}|} = \frac{1}{2}\sum_n \log{(1+\frac{1}{n^2})}
 \sum|\frac{1}{n^2}|
\log\left(1+\frac{i}{n}\right)\sim_\infty\frac i n
\log\left\vert 1+\frac{i}{n}\right\vert=\frac{1}{2}\log\left(1+\frac 1 {n^2}\right)\sim_\infty\frac{1}{2n^2}
